    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, so the paint is flawless and the interior still has that wonderful new-car smell. It drives like a dream and has been pampered with love since day one. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
